item.title: NARI
item.description: score:27 Chances: Inari Medical (NARI) has shown consistent revenue growth, with a 22.6% increase in Q4 2023. The two-year interim results from the CLOUT registry show significant improvement in patient outcomes, indicating the potential for continued success. Risks: Inari Medical’s operating losses widened in Q4 2023, which may raise concerns about the company’s profitability.
